Maintainer: Aaron Webster <awebster@gmail.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), dkms
Standards-Version: 4.6.2

Package: hid-playstation-edge-dkms
Architecture: all
Depends: dkms, ${misc:Depends}
Description: DualSense Edge extra buttons kernel module (DKMS)
 Patched hid-playstation kernel module that exposes the four extra
 buttons on the PlayStation DualSense Edge controller (product 0x0df2):
 Fn1, Fn2, left paddle, and right paddle as BTN_TRIGGER_HAPPY1-4.
 .
 This package uses DKMS to automatically rebuild the module for each
 installed kernel version.
